## Data Quality

| Field | Completeness | Notes |
|-------|--------------|-------|
| Title | 100% | ✓ All courses have titles |
| URL | 100% | ✓ All URLs valid and accessible |
| Description | 100% | ✓ Clean, concise descriptions |
| Learning Path | 100% | ✓ All courses categorized |
| Duration | 5% | ⚠️ Field captured too much page content |
| Level | 0% | ⚠️ Not consistently available |
| Price | 100% | ✓ All courses are free |
| Category | 100% | ✓ All Apache Airflow / Data Engineering |

**Overall Data Quality**: 65% - Core fields excellent, duration extraction needs refinement

