**Astronomer Academy** is a focused, high-quality training platform for Apache Airflow and data pipeline orchestration. With 59 course records (~40 unique) organized into structured learning paths, it provides comprehensive coverage of a single tool ecosystem.

**For LinkedIn Learning**:
- **Fit**: Niche technical content for data engineers
- **Value**: Deep Airflow expertise, well-structured curriculum
